If you do not want to rerun the notebook, use an anonymous artifact repository containing the final exported scales.

### Recommended anonymous repository option

Use:

- a **private OSF project**
- with an **anonymized view-only link**

Placeholder:

```text
ANON_REPO_URL=<paste your anonymized OSF view-only link here>
```

